õÇ®Y<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:5:"12005";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-05-20 01:52:58";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-05-20 01:52:58";s:12:"post_content";s:4974:"<p style="text-align: justify;">In these modern times, most of the big and small industries have developed social media strategies as most of the companies understand the importance of socializing and consult for the best social media management tools. The main aim of social media advertising is to engage with customers from every sector all over the world or with a particular target audience. It might be difficult for the small traders as they might not have sufficient budget to invest as much in social media. By using social media sites, you can reduce the pressure of many daily activities and that will help you when you need time to plan for your business growth. The following social media tools will help you to organize your day-to-day activities. Some of the following apps can be used by small traders.</p>
<!--more-->
<h2 style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Drum Up</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">By using Drum Up social media management tools, you can manage numerous accounts of your social media. It will work as the best management tool if you own a small business. It will help you to become consistent in your business after doing your day-to-day activities. Among the other social media management tools, this social media site also has some techniques which you can use to promote your ideas and business.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">In the Drum Up social media management tools, there are wider functions which will help you to create something new for your marketing purposes like sharing content, product pictures, or rearranging some topics. This app will even help you to get a new list of key words related to your business that you will find on the dashboard.Â  You can also add content feed. This app has hashtag features which can be used with the content posts and even if you want to make a custom post, you can make a list of those posts. One of the best features you will find in this app is that you can repost your content as many times as you want. As a result, you will not fall behind in the queue. Drum Up has a chrome edition which will let you add additional materials.</p>

<h2 style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>IFTTT</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This is one of the best social media management tools; by using IFTTT, you can save lots of time if you are a small trader. As a result, you can focus on other important activities. This app is created in such a way that it can help you to manage many things at the same time. For instance, if you have a website or blog, you can post and publish your content to social media like Facebook or Twitter. It will also work as a backup for saving photos to a Dropbox or to Google drive. It can sync all kinds of social media pictures and profiles as one platform. You will be astonished to learn that it is used by more than 280 channels for marketing.</p>

<h2 style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>RiteTag</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">RiteTag social media management tools work with more than 14 websites like Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Tweetdeck, etc. This app works best with Twitter. With a single click, you can post your content on Twitter. If you want a wider share of your link; You can use RiteTag on your image or on your content. The best thing on this social media site is that it shows hashtags which have the most popularity. If you want to, you can add it with RSS feeds.</p>

<h2 style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Commun.it</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This social media management tool is a related offshoot of Twitter and it has great value for the small business owner. It will help you to remove all kinds of unnecessary content from your social media dashboard. You can get the update from this significant website in your timeline without consulting other social media management tools. One of the best features of this social media site is that it suggests whom you should follow and whom you should not. It will show three important collections - Influencers, Supporters and Involved Members. For this reason, you will be able to identify your customers accurately.</p>

<h2 style="font-size: x-large;"><strong>Feedly</strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;">For every business, content creation is considered as one of the best business tools. Feedly works as the best app for selecting great content from the various sources on the Internet. Its RSS reader collects many sites according to your preference. For various purposes, you can add YouTube, blogs, etc. You can monitor your competitors and get current news about your firm with this app.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Finally, it can be said that social media sites are connecting audiences from all over the world; and that is the best thing for business owners who send product info to their target customers. Using such lovely social media management tools, you can save lots of time.</p>";s:10:"post_title";s:67:"5 Best Social Media Management Tools for 2017 to Grow Your Business";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:786:"In these modern times, most of the big and small industries have developed social media strategies as most of the companies understand the importance of socializing and consult for the best social media management tools. The main aim of social media advertising is to engage with customers from every sector all over the world or with a particular target audience. It might be difficult for the small traders as they might not have sufficient budget to invest as much in social media. By using social media sites, you can reduce the pressure of many daily activities and that will help you when you need time to plan for your business growth. The following social media tools will help you to organize your day-to-day activities. Some of the following apps can be used by small traders.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:55:"5-best-social-media-management-tools-2017-grow-business";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-06-20 04:41:02";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-06-20 04:41:02";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:45:"http://www.socialmedia-solutions.com/?p=12005";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}}